    <item>
      <title>卢拉巩固巴西央行转向持续 CPI 目标的决心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/lula-cements-brazil-central-bank-switch-to-continuous-cpi-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西正在改变其通胀目标制度，以设定一个连续时期而非日历年的目标，分析师预计此举将减少央行的政治噪音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/lula-cements-brazil-central-bank-switch-to-continuous-cpi-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:55:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元疲软为投资者避险提供另一个理由，导致美国国债价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/treasuries-slide-as-weak-yen-offers-another-reason-to-shun-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日元汇率的最新下滑加剧了债券投资者的焦虑，美国国债价格下跌，导致大多数国债收益率升至一周多以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/treasuries-slide-as-weak-yen-offers-another-reason-to-shun-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:11:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
